      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/655241647_18569119369010395_7374133086712181329_n.heic?stp=dst-jpg_e35_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=111&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1Njg0MzgxMzU3MDc4ODc1MQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjExNTJ4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=VuXNr0CHbyAQ7kNvwGP7Y_l&amp;_nc_oc=AdqHycTwojvXKZvOefzJi9cVnvyErDvhem7bIC3GUWyENMZ5ep2T-Y86cZTsFu24ANI&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=eJrVS1mdgnATdSbW48QpNw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyxHHnHm8xVIjbQXrau3RgdFSS77tBzCPMxqlYxTsA8ZQ&amp;oe=69CA0417" alt="Instagram billede fra @bronshojvandtaarn" /></p><p><strong>@bronshojvandtaarn</strong></p><p>On the 28th of March in Brønshøj Vandtårn we open the valve for boundary seeking artists and experimental ideas. Join us this evening for perfomances without the limitations of genre.<br/>
